RawLine: SKILL_120202_Tip,【{color=#FFD700}暗勁{/color}】\n相當容易中斷敵人動作，若以此招中斷敵人動作，會將敵人擊飛一段距離。傷害較低。,【{color=#FFD700}暗劲{/color}】\n相当容易中断敌人动作，若以此招中断敌人动作，会将敌人击飞一段距离。伤害较低。

Items.mt: <[>Dark Gust<]><<\n>>It is very easy to interrupt enemy movement, and if you interrupt enemy movement with this move, it will send them flying for a distance. Damage is low.
